=================
Chapel doc README
=================

This directory contains the following documentation:

README.building  : information about building the Chapel compiler
README.compiling : how to use the Chapel compiler to compile code

hpcc06.pdf : our report for the 2006 HPC Challenge competition
             (http://www.hpcchallenge.org), which also serves as a
             tutorial to Chapel via three of the HPCC benchmarks:
             STREAM Triad, Random Access, and FFT
